{# Domain-agnostic cover letter. Uses JD keywords + profile contact. #}
{% set kws = (job.ats_keywords or []) %}
Dear Hiring Team at {{ (job.company or '') | trim }},

I’m excited to apply for the **{{ (job.title or 'the role') | trim }}** position.

**Why I’m a fit**
- Background: {{ (profile.target_titles or []) | join(', ') if profile.target_titles else 'relevant experience' }}.
- Strengths aligned to your needs:
{%- if kws %}
{%- for kw in kws[:5] %}
  - {{ kw | capitalize }}
{%- endfor %}
{%- else %}
  - Relevant achievements and skills tailored to the job description.
{%- endif %}

I’d welcome the chance to share brief examples of related work and how I can contribute at {{ (job.company or 'your organization') | trim }}. Thank you for your time.

Best regards,

{{ profile.full_name or profile.name or '' }}
{{ profile.email or '' }}{% if profile.phone %} | {{ profile.phone }}{% endif %}
